mr.robotto.events

Class MrBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • mr.robotto.events.MrBundle

  • public class MrBundle
extends java.lang.Object
    Bundle to store multiple types of data. Used to pass data between an Android event received in a MrEventDispatcher and processed in a MrEventsListener
